#### PR description:

This PR removes the deprecated HLT plugin `PFJetsMatchedToFilteredCaloJetsProducer`. The latter has been replaced by `HLTPFJetsMatchedToFilteredCaloJetsProducer` in #37057 and #37474.

This cleanup is part of [CMSHLT-2244](https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-2244). No backports will be necessary.

Merely technical. No changes expected.

#### PR validation:

`./addOnTests.py` passed.
